  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 10th level, you've become adept acting as the passenger in the dark. </p><p>The stalker in the night. </p><p>The one who silences screams before they even echo from your targets lungs, all under the cover of the night, before anyone even knows you are there. </p><p>When you would score a Lethal attack against a creature marked as your Primary Target, using your Weapons of Darkness jutsu, while you are in Dim light or Darkness or they are blinded, you increase your Weapons of Darkness Damage die by 1 step.</p>",
